{"item_id":"f751883493:0","text":"RenderMan for Blender 可以在字符串参数中替换多种预定义 tokens。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:1","text":"它们可用于动画纹理序列、引用特定存储位置等。每个 token 都应包在一对尖括号内。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:2","text":"下面是默认 tokens 列表。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:3","text":"Token（令牌）"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:4","text":"含义"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:5","text":"<TEMP>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:6","text":"临时目录。在 Linux 和 macOS 上设置为 /tmp；在 Windows 上为 C:/tmp。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:7","text":"<OUT>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:8","text":"场景中所有生成文件的主根输出目录。可在 Workspace Editor（工作区编辑器）中设置。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:9","text":"<blend>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:10","text":"当前 blend 文件名。如果当前场景尚未保存，则设为 UNTITLED。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:11","text":"<blend_dir>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:12","text":"当前 blend 文件所在的目录。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:13","text":"<scene>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:14","text":"正在渲染的当前场景名称。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:15","text":"<layer>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:16","text":"正在渲染的当前视图层"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:17","text":"<aov>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:18","text":"AOV 名称"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:19","text":"<f4>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:20","text":"帧号填充；本例中为 4。若不需要填充可以省略，也可以使用更小数字。大写或小写的 'f' 都可识别。"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:21","text":"<ext>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:22","text":"文件类型扩展名"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:23","text":"<file>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:24","text":"这与上面的 <blend> 相同"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:25","text":"<version>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:26","text":"插入在 Workspace Editor（工作区编辑器）中指定的 version 编号"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:27","text":"<take>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:28","text":"插入在 Workspace Editor（工作区编辑器）中指定的 take 编号"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:29","text":"<date>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:30","text":"Current（当前）日期"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:31","text":"<frame>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:32","text":"十进制帧号"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:33","text":"<jobid>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:34","text":"唯一 job identifier（作业标识符）"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:35","text":"<time>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:36","text":"Current（当前）时间"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:37","text":"<ws>"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:38","text":"与上面的 <OUT> 相同"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:39","text":"还可以添加 Custom（自定义）用户 tokens（请参见"}
{"item_id":"f751883493:40","text":"Workspace Editor（工作区编辑器）"}
